#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:2
msgid "Analog"
msgstr "Analògic"

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:11
msgid ""
"The :mod:`qilisdk.analog` layer lets you build symbolic Hamiltonians and "
"time-dependent schedules that can be simulated or submitted to Qili "
"backends. Its core types are "
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Hamiltonian` and "
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`."
msgstr ""
"La capa :mod:`qilisdk.analog` permet construir Hamiltonians simbòlics i "
"esquemes dependents del temps que es poden simular o enviar als backends "
"de Qili. Els seus tipus principals són "
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Hamiltonian` i "
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`."

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:13
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Hamiltonian`: Tools to build "
"arbitrary Hamiltonians using symbolic Pauli operators."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Hamiltonian`: Eines per construir "
"Hamiltonians arbitraris utilitzant operadors de Pauli simbòlics."

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:14
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`: Flexible time-dependent "
"evolution with callable/interval coefficients and step/linear "
"interpolation."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`: Evolució flexible dependent "
"del temps amb coeficients callable/interval i interpolació "
"escalonada/lineal."

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:17
msgid "Hamiltonian"
msgstr "Hamiltonià"

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:19
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Hamiltonian` class represents a "
"symbolic Hamiltonian as a sum of weighted Pauli operators. You can create"
" Hamiltonians using the built-in Pauli operators and combine them with "
"standard arithmetic operations."
msgstr ""
"La classe :class:`~qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Hamiltonian` representa un "
"Hamiltonià simbòlic com una suma d'operadors de Pauli ponderats. Es poden"
" crear Hamiltonians utilitzant els operadors de Pauli integrats i "
"combinar-los amb operacions aritmètiques estàndard."

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:21
msgid "**Common constructors**"
msgstr "**Constructors comuns**"

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:23
msgid ""
"``X(i)``, ``Y(i)``, ``Z(i)``, ``I(i)`` produces a Hamiltonian with a "
"single-qubit Pauli."
msgstr ""
"``X(i)``, ``Y(i)``, ``Z(i)``, ``I(i)`` produeix un Hamiltonià amb un "
"Pauli d'un sol qubit."

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:24
msgid ""
"Construction using arithmetic operations. The operations follow Python "
"syntax, for example: ``2 * Z(0) + Z(1)`` and ``Z(0) * Z(1)`` build multi-"
"qubit Hamiltonian."
msgstr ""
"Construcció mitjançant operacions aritmètiques. Les operacions segueixen "
"la sintaxi de Python, per exemple: ``2 * Z(0) + Z(1)`` i ``Z(0) * Z(1)`` "
"construeixen Hamiltonians multi-qubit."

